1
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:28,200
My lord.

2
00:01:31,519 --> 00:01:32,680
My lord! My lord!

3
00:01:33,040 --> 00:01:33,319
Are you all right?

4
00:01:33,359 --> 00:01:35,840
Your bodies and names will perish,

5
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:39,280
but the river flows on for eternity.

6
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:40,280
Well said!

7
00:01:43,879 --> 00:01:44,319
Ning Chen.

8
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:46,000
Everything you have spoken of

9
00:01:46,359 --> 00:01:47,959
is merely your one-sided account.

10
00:01:48,040 --> 00:01:50,319
How are We to place trust in you?

11
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:54,840
Your Majesty, I beg to report.

12
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:58,079
The Chongzhou officials have confessed.

13
00:02:00,319 --> 00:02:01,239
Please review them, Your Majesty.

14
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:32,400
Are these still officials of Da Xuan?

15
00:02:33,120 --> 00:02:34,840
They're nothing but a pack of beasts!

16
00:02:36,439 --> 00:02:38,719
Inventing pretexts, disregarding lives,

17
00:02:38,879 --> 00:02:39,759
forcing decent women into prostitution.

18
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:42,599
Their crimes are too numerous to list.

19
00:02:43,199 --> 00:02:45,319
How dare they act so recklessly!

20
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:48,039
Your Majesty, they deserve death!

21
00:02:48,879 --> 00:02:49,400
Your Majesty,

22
00:02:50,080 --> 00:02:50,919
for such acts,

23
00:02:51,199 --> 00:02:53,159
only their deaths can appease the people.

24
00:02:54,759 --> 00:02:56,199
We beg Your Majesty to issue the decree

25
00:02:56,520 --> 00:02:59,120
and give the people of the realm justice.

26
00:02:59,879 --> 00:03:01,560
We second the motion.

27
00:03:05,520 --> 00:03:06,120
Minister Qian,

28
00:03:06,879 --> 00:03:07,840
you just said

29
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:11,280
the people of Chongzhou lived in peace.

30
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:14,400
Your Majesty,

31
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:16,800
I was momentarily confused.

32
00:03:17,080 --> 00:03:19,439
I beg Your Majesty for mercy!

33
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:21,439
Confused?

34
00:03:22,000 --> 00:03:23,879
Just how much did you take from them?

35
00:03:24,360 --> 00:03:24,800
Guards!

36
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:27,960
Throw Qian Xingguo into prison.

37
00:03:28,159 --> 00:03:30,560
Imperial Inspectorate, investigate the Ministry of Revenue at once,

38
00:03:31,120 --> 00:03:33,879
and prosecute all involved in the Chongzhou case.

39
00:03:35,280 --> 00:03:36,599
I obey the decree.

40
00:03:37,159 --> 00:03:39,319
Your Majesty, spare me!

41
00:03:40,159 --> 00:03:41,560
Your Majesty!

42
00:03:42,439 --> 00:03:43,960
Your Majesty!

43
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:48,319
Your Majesty,

44
00:03:48,599 --> 00:03:49,280
I believe

45
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:51,960
the Imperial Uncle enraged heaven and men.

46
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:53,800
Ning Chen's offense doesn't warrant death.

47
00:03:54,159 --> 00:03:55,759
I beg Your Majesty to show mercy.

48
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:56,960
Your Majesty,

49
00:03:57,280 --> 00:04:00,439
Ning Chen acted to defend royal honor.

50
00:04:00,759 --> 00:04:03,680
I also feel he does not deserve death.

51
00:04:04,080 --> 00:04:04,719
Your Majesty,

52
00:04:05,319 --> 00:04:07,080
Ning Chen excels in both letters and arms,

53
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:08,360
brimming with talent.

54
00:04:08,719 --> 00:04:10,719
He may truly be the Poet Immortal reborn.

55
00:04:11,159 --> 00:04:14,199
He will surely become a pillar of Da Xuan.

56
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:16,279
If we execute him today,

57
00:04:16,759 --> 00:04:19,319
it would be a great loss to our literature.

58
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:23,319
I implore Your Majesty for leniency.

59
00:04:23,959 --> 00:04:25,720
I second the motion.

60
00:04:28,439 --> 00:04:31,120
What a fine performance indeed.

61
00:04:31,839 --> 00:04:33,720
Truly worthy of Your Majesty.

62
00:04:34,399 --> 00:04:35,439
This round,

63
00:04:36,199 --> 00:04:37,360
I've lost.

64
00:04:38,439 --> 00:04:38,959
Left Chancellor,

65
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:41,439
you are head of all officials.

66
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:43,680
What is your view on this matter?

67
00:04:44,879 --> 00:04:45,879
I beg to report, Your Majesty,

68
00:04:46,759 --> 00:04:47,639
I believe

69
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:50,000
the other ministers are absolutely right.

70
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:52,160
Though Ning Chen slew the Imperial Uncle,

71
00:04:52,319 --> 00:04:54,279
there was due cause.

72
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:56,639
He deserves a lenient sentence.

73
00:04:57,759 --> 00:04:59,079
The Left Chancellor makes a fair point.

74
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:03,120
It seems justice lives in people's hearts.

75
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:04,879
Ning Chen.

76
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:07,120
I have a few words

77
00:05:07,639 --> 00:05:08,959
I'd like to share with all the ministers.

78
00:05:10,279 --> 00:05:11,319
The salary you receive,

79
00:05:12,079 --> 00:05:13,360
is the people's flesh and blood.

80
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:15,959
The common folk may be easy to oppress,

81
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:18,120
but heaven cannot be deceived.

82
00:05:18,879 --> 00:05:20,160
We are all subjects,

83
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:22,519
living on the sovereign's salary.

84
00:05:23,399 --> 00:05:25,879
We must fulfill our duties faithfully

85
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:30,000
and ease His Majesty's burdens.

86
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:32,800
That flattery he just dished out,

87
00:05:33,079 --> 00:05:34,920
is on a whole other level than mine.

88
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:37,399
Well said!

89
00:05:37,639 --> 00:05:40,199
Ministers, bear Ning Chen's words in mind,

90
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:42,839
and do not disappoint Us again.

91
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:46,199
We shall engrave them in our hearts,

92
00:05:46,560 --> 00:05:49,160
and not fail Your Majesty's grace.

93
00:05:49,519 --> 00:05:50,120
Ning Chen,

94
00:05:50,519 --> 00:05:53,399
although the ministers all plead for you,

95
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:55,000
you struck down the Imperial Uncle,

96
00:05:55,360 --> 00:05:57,480
slighting the royal family's dignity.

97
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:58,839
The death penalty may be spared,

98
00:05:59,319 --> 00:06:01,480
but your crime cannot go unpunished.

99
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:04,360
What's he up to now?

100
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:08,199
When we discussed saving him in the study,

101
00:06:08,439 --> 00:06:09,879
this wasn't part of the plan.

102
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:13,480
The Tuluo Kingdom often raids our borders.

103
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:15,360
This matter is like a stubborn disease.

104
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:17,920
Your previous strategy was effective,

105
00:06:18,279 --> 00:06:19,879
but it is not a permanent cure.

106
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:21,600
If you can devise a way

107
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:23,959
to keep our border safe this winter,

108
00:06:24,240 --> 00:06:27,079
We will not only pardon all your crimes,

109
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:28,800
but also reward you.

110
00:06:29,199 --> 00:06:29,800
Ning Chen,

111
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:33,519
are you willing to redeem through merit?

112
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:41,399
A newborn calf fears no tiger.

113
00:06:41,879 --> 00:06:44,000
The entire court has no solution.

114
00:06:44,439 --> 00:06:47,040
What can a mere youth possibly do?

115
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:48,360
The cavalry of the Tuluo Kingdom

116
00:06:48,879 --> 00:06:51,319
has long been a grave threat to Us.

117
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:53,160
If you are unwilling to go,

118
00:06:54,079 --> 00:06:55,839
We shall not force you.

119
00:06:56,879 --> 00:06:57,639
When that time comes,

120
00:06:58,000 --> 00:06:59,240
We shall have no choice

121
00:07:00,959 --> 00:07:02,800
but to lead a Personal Campaign.

122
00:07:03,079 --> 00:07:05,439
Your Majesty, this must not be!

123
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:06,120
Your Majesty.

124
00:07:06,519 --> 00:07:07,839
The battlefield changes in an instant.

125
00:07:08,000 --> 00:07:09,160
Your priceless body

126
00:07:09,279 --> 00:07:10,680
must not be put in harm's way.

127
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:13,120
Please rescind this decree, Your Majesty.

128
00:07:13,279 --> 00:07:16,079
Please rescind this decree, Your Majesty.

129
00:07:18,399 --> 00:07:19,160
Ning Chen.

130
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:24,120
His Majesty is someone who,

131
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:27,800
With the pen, he brings peace to the realm;

132
00:07:28,759 --> 00:07:32,360
on horseback, he secures the empire.

133
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:34,759
What the hell is the Tuluo Kingdom?

134
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:37,120
Are they worth a Personal Campaign?

135
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:38,959
That would be flattering them too much.

136
00:07:39,759 --> 00:07:40,199
Your Majesty.

137
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:41,560
This subject

138
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:43,759
is willing to go to the frontier.

139
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:45,399
If I fail to handle the Tuluo Kingdom,

140
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:46,879
I vow never to return to the capital.

141
00:07:47,079 --> 00:07:47,600
Excellent.

142
00:07:48,759 --> 00:07:52,199
Then We shall await good news here.

143
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:59,800
Court is dismissed.

144
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:04,199
Long live Your Majesty!

145
00:08:29,199 --> 00:08:30,000
Ning Chen.

146
00:08:30,399 --> 00:08:32,279
Drop by my residence sometime.

147
00:08:32,919 --> 00:08:33,840
I'll be sure to visit when I'm free.

148
00:08:39,159 --> 00:08:40,120
Old General Chen.

149
00:08:40,519 --> 00:08:41,759
Thank you for helping me today,

150
00:08:41,919 --> 00:08:43,080
otherwise I'd be done for.

151
00:08:43,759 --> 00:08:46,360
Thanking me with mere words won't do.

152
00:08:46,519 --> 00:08:49,159
I want fine wine from Zhuangyuan Tower.

153
00:08:49,679 --> 00:08:50,440
As much as you can drink.

154
00:08:53,879 --> 00:08:54,639
Lord Ning.

155
00:08:55,399 --> 00:08:56,440
Congratulations.

156
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:58,000
You've raised your son well.

157
00:08:58,200 --> 00:09:00,519
I must seek your advice someday.

158
00:09:01,159 --> 00:09:02,240
My useless son

159
00:09:02,399 --> 00:09:03,519
can't do anything right,

160
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:04,679
and only knows how to eat.

161
00:09:05,639 --> 00:09:07,399
Truly, like father, like son.

162
00:09:07,759 --> 00:09:09,440
Lord Ning has brilliant literary talent,

163
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:11,720
and your son is even more gifted.

164
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,120
How enviable.

165
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:15,200
You flatter me.

166
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:17,840
I thought he was as good as dead,

167
00:09:18,200 --> 00:09:20,919
who knew he'd be the Poet Immortal reborn.

168
00:09:21,519 --> 00:09:22,639
Skilled in both letters and arms.

169
00:09:23,279 --> 00:09:24,519
He's finally brought me honor.

170
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:25,960
Chen'er.

171
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:27,840
Come here, come here.

172
00:09:29,279 --> 00:09:30,320
Are we that close?

173
00:09:30,799 --> 00:09:32,200
A scumbag who abandons wife and children,

174
00:09:32,759 --> 00:09:34,919
yet you have the nerve to cozy up to me.

175
00:09:36,759 --> 00:09:37,559
My lords,

176
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:39,480
I have some matters to attend to,

177
00:09:39,519 --> 00:09:40,399
so I'll be taking my leave.

178
00:09:41,960 --> 00:09:42,399
Goodbye.

179
00:09:43,399 --> 00:09:44,960
I'm getting on in years,

180
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,840
I really shouldn't be walking backwards.

181
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:48,799
Well...

182
00:09:50,799 --> 00:09:51,960
Lord Ning's lawful wife

183
00:09:52,320 --> 00:09:53,879
is the Left Chancellor's daughter.

184
00:09:54,120 --> 00:09:57,159
Why talk of 'abandon wife and children'?

185
00:09:57,799 --> 00:10:00,519
I heard Lord Ning has three sons.

186
00:10:00,879 --> 00:10:03,120
Which one of them is Ning Chen?

187
00:10:03,879 --> 00:10:06,279
I've met all three of Lord Ning's sons.

188
00:10:06,519 --> 00:10:07,960
There's no Silver Guard Ning among them.

189
00:10:08,799 --> 00:10:09,360
Lord Ning,

190
00:10:09,679 --> 00:10:11,440
who is Silver Guard Ning's mother?

191
00:10:11,919 --> 00:10:14,679
I never heard you took a concubine either.

192
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:15,480
Indeed.

193
00:10:16,559 --> 00:10:17,080
Farewell.

194
00:10:17,919 --> 00:10:18,679
Farewell, farewell.

195
00:10:21,600 --> 00:10:22,720
Damned bastard.

196
00:10:23,159 --> 00:10:23,919
Utterly disgraceful.

197
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:27,440
If rivals know I abandon wife and children,

198
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:28,799
and impeach me,

199
00:10:29,679 --> 00:10:31,240
with His Majesty's favor toward Ning Chen,

200
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:34,240
my days as Minister of Rites are numbered.

201
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:41,480
The old ginger really is the spiciest.

202
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:42,480
Old General Chen,

203
00:10:43,879 --> 00:10:46,559
I have plenty of ginger and chili at home.

204
00:10:46,919 --> 00:10:48,600
And undiluted wine too,

205
00:10:48,759 --> 00:10:49,320
as much as you'd like.

206
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:51,720
I must visit and taste them someday.

207
00:10:51,879 --> 00:10:52,440
Absolutely.

208
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:56,399
Greetings, Old General Chen.

209
00:10:57,559 --> 00:10:59,360
Greetings, Crown Prince.

210
00:11:05,519 --> 00:11:06,120
You two chat.

211
00:11:10,200 --> 00:11:11,919
Crown Prince, do you need something?

212
00:11:12,519 --> 00:11:13,919
Congratulations, Ning Chen.

213
00:11:14,799 --> 00:11:16,279
Do you know that your acquittal this time,

214
00:11:16,559 --> 00:11:17,600
besides Father's mercy

215
00:11:17,759 --> 00:11:18,919
and the ministers' pleas,

216
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:20,960
also owes thanks to Princess Huai'an?

217
00:11:22,399 --> 00:11:23,159
Princess Huai'an?

218
00:11:24,879 --> 00:11:27,480
She actually pleaded for me?

219
00:11:30,440 --> 00:11:31,799
I asked her to.

220
00:11:34,039 --> 00:11:35,080
After you slew the Imperial Uncle,

221
00:11:35,399 --> 00:11:37,399
Father was in a foul mood for days.

222
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:38,679
I didn't dare approach him,

223
00:11:39,279 --> 00:11:42,120
so I had Princess Huai'an plead for you.

224
00:11:42,799 --> 00:11:43,840
You didn't dare go,

225
00:11:44,159 --> 00:11:45,960
so you pushed your own sister out there?

226
00:11:46,320 --> 00:11:46,879
Let's go.

227
00:11:47,440 --> 00:11:48,399
A debt for saving your life

228
00:11:48,679 --> 00:11:50,200
is best repaid in person.

229
00:11:50,759 --> 00:11:51,360
I'll take you to her.

230
00:11:56,159 --> 00:11:56,960
I'm coming to catch you!

231
00:11:58,120 --> 00:11:58,679
Princess!

232
00:12:04,519 --> 00:12:05,200
I caught you!

233
00:12:14,600 --> 00:12:15,720
You stink so bad!

234
00:12:16,320 --> 00:12:17,720
This girl's doing it on purpose.

235
00:12:18,159 --> 00:12:19,440
I just haven't bathed for a few days.

236
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:21,799
You reek!

237
00:12:22,720 --> 00:12:23,279
What's wrong with you?

238
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:24,759
Did you fall into a latrine or something?

239
00:12:26,320 --> 00:12:27,080
So young,

240
00:12:27,279 --> 00:12:28,320
yet your tongue's so sharp.

241
00:12:28,519 --> 00:12:29,320
Say that again, I dare you.

242
00:12:30,639 --> 00:12:33,480
He was in the Imperial Inspectorate prison.

243
00:12:33,759 --> 00:12:35,080
He was only pardoned and released today.

244
00:12:35,399 --> 00:12:36,879
He hasn't had time to bathe or change.

245
00:12:37,480 --> 00:12:38,879
A bit of an odor is unavoidable.

246
00:12:40,720 --> 00:12:41,480
Brother Crown Prince,

247
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:42,720
what brings you here today?

248
00:12:43,279 --> 00:12:45,159
You pleaded for Ning Chen earlier.

249
00:12:45,480 --> 00:12:47,759
He came today especially to thank you.

250
00:12:52,200 --> 00:12:54,000
Thank you for speaking up, Princess.

251
00:12:56,600 --> 00:12:57,440
Well, tell me,

252
00:12:58,039 --> 00:12:59,039
how do you plan to thank me?

253
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:05,919
I have no power or influence,

254
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:09,360
and truly nothing worthy to offer.

255
00:13:09,600 --> 00:13:10,639
If the Princess doesn't mind,

256
00:13:10,799 --> 00:13:11,559
let me treat you to a meal.

257
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:14,480
As if I need a meal from you.

258
00:13:15,120 --> 00:13:16,440
But I'm so poor,

259
00:13:16,759 --> 00:13:18,960
what could I possibly offer the Princess?

260
00:13:20,279 --> 00:13:23,200
You're not as handsome as my royal father,

261
00:13:23,679 --> 00:13:25,360
nor as tall as my royal brother,

262
00:13:26,679 --> 00:13:27,799
and as for personality,

263
00:13:28,240 --> 00:13:29,320
compared to mine,

264
00:13:29,679 --> 00:13:30,639
yours falls far short.

265
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:33,360
But they say you're brilliantly talented.

266
00:13:33,799 --> 00:13:34,320
How about this?

267
00:13:34,799 --> 00:13:36,159
Write a poem for me.

268
00:13:39,799 --> 00:13:40,279
What?

269
00:13:40,840 --> 00:13:42,039
Am I not worthy of one?

270
00:13:42,480 --> 00:13:43,840
You're worthy, absolutely.

271
00:13:44,039 --> 00:13:44,480
You!

272
00:13:45,279 --> 00:13:46,919
The Princess is worthy.

273
00:13:48,279 --> 00:13:51,559
I was just deep in thought.

274
00:13:52,639 --> 00:13:54,000
You really want a poem on the spot?

275
00:13:55,480 --> 00:13:56,360
Let me warn you,

276
00:13:56,720 --> 00:13:58,200
if you dare to slack off,

277
00:13:58,559 --> 00:14:00,559
I'll have you caned.

278
00:14:01,799 --> 00:14:02,720
That's right, Ning Chen.

279
00:14:03,159 --> 00:14:05,879
You're known as the Poet Immortal reborn.

280
00:14:06,320 --> 00:14:08,039
If the poem you give Princess Huai'an

281
00:14:08,360 --> 00:14:09,320
fails to please her,

282
00:14:09,960 --> 00:14:11,399
your Poet Immortal title

283
00:14:11,679 --> 00:14:12,759
will be ruined.

284
00:14:15,799 --> 00:14:16,600
That won't happen.

285
00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:24,480
Princess, please listen well.

286
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:31,799
Clouds long for her raiment, flowers for her face;

287
00:14:32,279 --> 00:14:37,080
Spring breeze caresses the rail, dew-drenched with grace.

288
00:14:39,039 --> 00:14:40,000
And the next two lines?

289
00:14:40,519 --> 00:14:43,639
If not seen atop the jade mountains' crest,

290
00:14:45,879 --> 00:14:51,879
Then 'neath the moon on Jasper Terrace she'd rest.

291
00:14:53,879 --> 00:14:54,799
What a magnificent poem!

292
00:14:54,960 --> 00:14:56,720
The Poet Immortal reborn, indeed.

293
00:14:57,120 --> 00:14:58,120
So beautiful, Ning Chen.

294
00:14:58,679 --> 00:15:00,240
How does that little head of yours work?

295
00:15:00,679 --> 00:15:02,120
How can you write such beautiful poetry?

296
00:15:03,559 --> 00:15:04,320
Besides,

297
00:15:04,639 --> 00:15:06,559
am I really as beautiful as you describe?

298
00:15:07,799 --> 00:15:09,000
You're making me blush.

299
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:12,480
I don't see

300
00:15:12,679 --> 00:15:14,679
a hint of a blush on you.

301
00:15:18,799 --> 00:15:19,759
As long as the Princess is pleased.

302
00:15:21,440 --> 00:15:22,039
Ning Chen,

303
00:15:22,679 --> 00:15:24,720
can you write a poem for me too?

304
00:15:25,639 --> 00:15:26,200
Come on, come on.

305
00:15:27,960 --> 00:15:29,240
Have you no shame?

306
00:15:29,440 --> 00:15:30,480
The Princess is a young lady,

307
00:15:30,600 --> 00:15:32,240
so a poem to please her is fitting.

308
00:15:32,440 --> 00:15:34,519
A grown man like you wants a freebie?

309
00:15:36,519 --> 00:15:37,039
Your Highness,

310
00:15:37,840 --> 00:15:40,000
my inspiration is exhausted today.

311
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:41,720
How about another day?

312
00:15:44,600 --> 00:15:45,120
Fine then.

313
00:15:45,559 --> 00:15:47,320
I'll keep this in mind.

314
00:15:48,919 --> 00:15:50,159
You owe me one poem.

315
00:15:52,799 --> 00:15:53,279
Attendants!

316
00:15:53,879 --> 00:15:55,639
Quickly write down Ning Chen's poem.

317
00:15:55,919 --> 00:15:56,799
I want to show it to Father.

318
00:15:57,600 --> 00:15:58,200
Yes.

319
00:16:19,559 --> 00:16:20,639
Greetings, Your Highness the Crown Prince.

320
00:16:21,519 --> 00:16:22,519
What brings you here?

321
00:16:23,039 --> 00:16:24,720
By order of the Empress,

322
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:26,279
I'm to summon Silver Guard Ning.

323
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:28,519
Me?

324
00:16:31,960 --> 00:16:33,200
What if I don't go?

325
00:16:33,840 --> 00:16:34,320
You must.

326
00:16:34,879 --> 00:16:35,759
When the Empress summons,

327
00:16:35,960 --> 00:16:36,600
you must go.

328
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:37,559
Don't worry.

329
00:16:37,759 --> 00:16:39,360
I'll accompany you there.

330
00:16:39,559 --> 00:16:40,000
Your Highness,

331
00:16:40,679 --> 00:16:41,759
the Empress instructed

332
00:16:42,039 --> 00:16:43,120
that she will see Ning Chen alone.

